係OPEN SOURCE, 一早係GITHUB都有得DOWNLOAD 可以FLASH落個FLIGHT CONTROL, 連CHROME都有APP可以用黎SET機, 只係DJI包裝好晒姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9067b4a3810d581b7e88028c58fd3d3e72b07d6b","tid":303220,"uid":7145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心一問 除咗支那機 有咩外國牌子嘅航拍機好用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己買PARTS砌</blockquote><br />\n有冇教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nGoPro karma?"},{"pid":"5804890109b8ad2ee7b86a0bb5c110c5f8a7188d","tid":303220,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:08:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心一問 除咗支那機 有咩外國牌子嘅航拍機好用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己買PARTS砌</blockquote><br />\n有冇教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過家下都9成9係大陸牌子, 你去外國網站訂果D, 都係同你係淘寶買完再訂返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你想玩邊D先? DRONE, 航拍定玩飛機?<br />\n<br />\nDRONE係細機好似空中四驅車咁, 淨機我估都2000, + remote又4,5百都OK + 即時影像又100左右<br />\n<br />\n航拍都係5千樓上, 飛機就最低玩, 2千樓下<br />\n<br />\n好多野好貴, remote由幾百都過萬既futaba又有, 叉電機又貴, 去10A以上既又2,3千一台, 你玩航拍果D如果用2,3百果D叉機, 一日只係叉到一舊電, 你有4,5舊都叉你幾日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a202123a93e5d2190abaa21e8c821ea15ae05dfc","tid":303220,"uid":5524,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一個牌子係唔同地方個管理方式都唔同，不嬲dji 係香港都有禁飛區，只係今次範圍改大左，佢改得，個產品條款肯定有明示暗示佢有咁ge ge 權力。<br />\n<br />\n同佢屌得果d 人都係業餘玩下，真係做野果d 一早就check 哂，唔會係呢d 時間飛，仲有拍戲係會用dji, 當然會用其他牌子，但dji 佔大數係hk, 同埋冇人理鳩你監唔監控，隻機點lock 唔係靠上網，係靠gps,你用佢個app 飛，佢個app 個map 就會有禁飛區，自然飛唔到，好簡單唔洗理咩點控制咁多機唔俾飛。</blockquote><br />\n其實今次禁飛區大左係政府自己訂出黎，維港個禁飛區大到去油麻地個邊都飛唔到，同埋DJI其實都保障左啲人亂鳩咁飛，因為公安出埋無線電黎干擾你，你照飛一陣炸撚左機仲大鑊。學你咁講，做野個啲一早check好曬邊到飛得，就算連普通玩機個班正常呢幾日都應該忍手唔飛住，無謂搞到機都無撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6acee8f600e346a03f2670698ede5483807394e","tid":303220,"uid":15078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:15:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67f9e93c5b1f3e7fbbe4c5b478193b5b08095fa0","tid":303220,"uid":120205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:18:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心一問 除咗支那機 有咩外國牌子嘅航拍機好用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己買PARTS砌</blockquote><br />\n有冇教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過家下都9成9係大陸牌子, 你去外國網站訂果D, 都係同你係淘寶買完再訂返黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你想玩邊D先? DRONE, 航拍定玩飛機?<br />\n<br />\nDRONE係細機好似空中四驅車咁, 淨機我估都2000, + remote又4,5百都OK + 即時影像又100左右<br />\n<br />\n航拍都係5千樓上, 飛機就最低玩, 2千樓下<br />\n<br />\n好多野好貴, remote由幾百都過萬既futaba又有, 叉電機又貴, 去10A以上既又2,3千一台, 你玩航拍果D如果用2,3百果D叉機, 一日只係叉到一舊電, 你有4,5舊都叉你幾日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打好熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以開po教人 留tg都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0458ef7f25d60560d23f0440ab4f557d49b03f1","tid":303220,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T06:20:53.000Z","msg":"習大大黎香港就玩少幾日啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ec1e4a9eddc5b7747812d3bb110c96278c6d9b","tid":303220,"uid":54183,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedB